# Runbook

> Operational playbook. AI agents debugging an outage retrieve by
> *symptom*, not by cause — section headers below follow that pattern
> intentionally.

## Operational invariants

> What MUST be true for this system to be healthy. Each invariant
> reads as a single declarative sentence.

* **<Invariant 1>** — one sentence.
* **<Invariant 2>** — one sentence.
* **<Invariant 3>** — one sentence.

A break of any invariant is an incident, even if no user has reported.

## Routine procedures

### Deploy

> Standard deploy command + expected duration + how to verify success.

### Rollback

> Rollback command + criteria for triggering it + verification.

### Restart

> Service restart procedure (graceful + forceful).

### Scale up / scale down

> Procedure + capacity ceilings + cost notes.

## Incident response

